title: Skins S07 Season 7 DVDRip XviD-HAGGiS [MED]
description:
All six episodes of the seventh and final series of the drama about the chaotic lives and loves of a group of young people. 
This time round the show follows three characters from previous series - Effy (Kaya Scodelario), Cassie (Hannah Murray) and Cook (Jack O'Connell). 
Having moved on from college they are now dealing with the pressures and dangers of the real world. 
The episodes are: 'Fire: Part 1', 'Fire: Part 2', 'Pure: Part 1', 'Pure: Part 2', 'Rise: Part 1' and 'Rise: Part 2'.
